        {
          "source": "emilkowalski",
          "text": "Accessibility. `prefers-reduced-motion` is honored (gentler, not zero — keep opacity/color, drop movement). Hover animations are gated behind `@media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine)`.",
          "suggestedId": "emilkowalski-accessibility-is-honored-gentler-not-zero",
          "category": "animations",
          "tags": [
            "motion",
            "animations"
          ],
          "bestMatch": 0.15
        },
        {
          "source": "emilkowalski",
          "text": "Interruptibility. Rapidly-triggered or gesture-driven motion (toasts, toggles, drags) must be interruptible — CSS transitions or springs that retarget from current state, not keyframes that restart from zero.",
          "suggestedId": "emilkowalski-interruptibility-rapidly-triggered-or-gesture-driven",
          "category": "animations",
          "tags": [
            "motion",
            "animations"
          ],
          "bestMatch": 0.16
        },
        {
          "source": "emilkowalski",
          "text": "Accessibility & cohesion — add reduced-motion + hover gating; tune to match the component's personality.",
