          ],
          "bestMatch": 0.18
        },
        {
          "source": "emilkowalski",
          "text": "Approve — no feel-breaking regressions, no obvious motion that should be deleted, durations and easing within bounds, interruptibility handled where needed, reduced-motion respected.",
